  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c82bf7a2-f072-4fc2-a29b-58f3e7f63dc8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a2950d99-6b80-403a-99af-14cc124469e2\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a0ad77d9-7130-4c94-88a0-990c3d320102\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 21</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-02095816-0b46-4466-a7f0-342971ad9f67\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6724b903-d3fa-4a3c-8c08-95144e19854e\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-98c64016-b7a7-46be-8fb3-dd10ec555906\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2dbef20e-c748-4f91-9961-feb6c4ee80f9\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[요소정리]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f3e1d0dd-24a6-4161-967f-4ca99977fa82\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-eebcc498-750e-4505-a731-3734b7763806\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>앞으로 7일간은 주문에 필요한 인쇄의 기본적인 요소를 정리하는 시간을 갖도록 하겠습니다. 27년의 인쇄 노하우를 가진 제가 좋은 자료를 만들기 위해 본격적으로 정리한 것이니 잘 읽어보시고 인쇄 주문이나 발주시 참고하셨으면 합니다. 이제 개발자에게 전달할 스토리 보드를 작성 하면서 본격적인 개발문서 작업에 들어갑니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9491e02e-11f8-4e3c-9137-15aab4509310\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4aa34970-4631-455c-97fc-2943a6073e29\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0e4a9505-b97b-4866-889a-240e5d5179f6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-446e92ae-4bc1-43be-b1ea-4cc67c0e569f\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c4e29d79-91f3-4de9-93ae-a81022825dd0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-52c2221f-fd47-4068-b19e-b5c93e89add0\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>제 사전에 실패는 있습니다. 하지만 시도가 없지는 않을 겁니다. 그것도 끊임없이요.~</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-df632a3f-73ad-4e88-b807-59128707a503\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cc7663a9-4860-42ca-b847-7a547fd8237e\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-111612d1-8290-4b24-9c68-7d3f5530da99\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3315458d-5731-4ea2-bbe8-2f420708722b\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-8ff7647e-5b51-4a06-a625-0e04cd076068\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e593bc7-7be7-4757-8729-d74632596aec\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5bfac177-007c-429f-b5df-98a805dbbb14\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>스토리보드 작성 예시</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb1b15a0-69a4-4f9c-a263-451eaf224195\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-26c1191a-d28a-4b38-bbe7-115fb489f4df\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4ad534f8-487a-40da-8d84-294f82cd0aeb\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니에서 준비한 소나기 프로젝트의 ppt 스토리보드를 하나만 이미지로 보여드리겠습니다. 1차로 작업한 예시이며 미완성된 작업입니다. 2차 개발 작업시 보강계획을 가지고 있지만 일단 이미지만 보시면 저의 스토리보드 작성에 대한 느낌을 이해하실 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4ba8e656-3b75-427a-9fd6-df7010a84c1c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222900020792/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9227d8d7-d484-440d-a482-aa723ebec612\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"S